        <qualifiedname>media_proxy_pl_calls::set_track_position</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Set Track Position. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Set the playing position of the media player in the current track. The position is given in hundredths of a second, from the beginning of the track of the track for positive values, and (backwards) from the end of the track for negative values.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>position</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The player position to set </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
